.SH "NAME"
i3blocks-monit \- i3blocks bar block for monit services.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fIi3blocks\-monit\fP [OPTION=value] [...]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
Report a summary of monit(1) service states. The output is in pango format and
suitable for i3blocks(1). Options can be
specified as environment variables or on the command line as \fIOPTION=value\fP.
.SH "OPTIONS"
.sp
\fBSTYLE_UP\fP=attributes
.RS 4
The \c
.URL "https://docs.gtk.org/Pango/pango_markup.html#the\-span\-attributes" "span attributes"
to apply to the number of up services.
.RE
.sp
\fBSTYLE_UMON\fP=attributes
.RS 4
The \c
.URL "https://docs.gtk.org/Pango/pango_markup.html#the\-span\-attributes" "span attributes"
to apply to the number of unmonitored services.
.RE
.sp
\fBSTYLE_DOWN\fP=attributes
.RS 4
The \c
.URL "https://docs.gtk.org/Pango/pango_markup.html#the\-span\-attributes" "span attributes"
to apply to the number of down services.
.RE
.sp
\fBSTYLE_INIT\fP=attributes
.RS 4
The \c
.URL "https://docs.gtk.org/Pango/pango_markup.html#the\-span\-attributes" "span attributes"
to apply to the number of initialising services.
.RE
.sp
\fBLABEL_UP\fP=label
.RS 4
The label to use for up services.
.RE
.sp
\fBLABEL_UMON\fP=label
.RS 4
The label to use for unmonitored services.
.RE
.sp
\fBLABEL_DOWN\fP=label
.RS 4
The label to use for down services.
.RE
.sp
\fBLABEL_INIT\fP=label
.RS 4
The label to use for initialising services.
.RE
.sp
\fBORDER\fP=list
.RS 4
A space\-delimited list indicating the order in which to display
\f(CRup\fP, \f(CRunmonitored\fP, \f(CRdown\fP, and \f(CRinitialising\fP services.
.RE
.sp
\fBSHOW_LABELS\fP=boolean
.RS 4
\f(CR1\fP to show labels, \f(CR0\fP to suppress labels.
.RE
.sp
\fBSHOW_ZEROS\fP=boolean
.RS 4
\f(CR1\fP to show states with 0 total services, \f(CR0\fP to suppress them.
.RE
.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
i3blocks config with default values:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
[monit]
command=i3blocks\-monit
markup=pango
interval=3600
STYLE_UP=weight=\*(Aqbold\*(Aq background=\*(Aq#009000\*(Aq color=\*(Aq#FFFFFF\*(Aq
STYLE_UMON=weight=\*(Aqbold\*(Aq background=\*(Aq#F0F000\*(Aq color=\*(Aq#000000\*(Aq
STYLE_DOWN=weight=\*(Aqbold\*(Aq background=\*(Aq#900000\*(Aq color=\*(Aq#FFFFFF\*(Aq
STYLE_INIT=weight=\*(Aqbold\*(Aq background=\*(Aq#C09000\*(Aq color=\*(Aq#FFFFFF\*(Aq
LABEL_UP=UP
LABEL_UMON=UMON
LABEL_DOWN=DOWN
LABEL_INIT=INIT
ORDER=up unmonitored down initialising
SHOW_LABELS=1
SHOW_ZEROS=1
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
Nagios\-like labels:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
[monit]
command=i3blocks\-monit
markup=pango
interval=3600
LABEL_UP=OK
LABEL_UMON=WARN
LABEL_DOWN=CRIT
LABEL_INIT=UNKN
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
Minimal display:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
[monit]
command=i3blocks\-monit
markup=pango
interval=3600
SHOW_LABELS=0
SHOW_ZEROS=0
.fam
.fi
